---
layout: base.njk
title: "About"
description: "About the designer and how to get in touch."
---

<section style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--deep); padding: 5rem 2rem 5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
  <div aria-hidden="true" style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: -10%; width: 500px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,77,28,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none;"></div>

  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: start;">
    <div class="fu">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">About Me</p>
      <h1 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5.5vw, 4.5rem); margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        Designer.<br /><em>Systems</em><br />thinker.
      </h1>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem;">
        <p style="color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.85;">{{ site.bio }}</p>
        <p style="color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.85;">Design is most powerful when it's invisible — when a brand feels inevitable, a product feels frictionless, a system runs without a second thought.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.85;">With a background spanning visual identity, no-code platforms, and industrial process design, I bring a product mindset to every brief.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fu fu1">
      <!-- Portrait placeholder -->
      <div style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); aspect-ratio: 3/4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <span class="label">Your photo here</span>
      </div>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <td class="label" style="padding: 1rem 0; width: 45%;">Based in</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem 0; color: var(--bright); font-weight: 600;">Your City</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <td class="label" style="padding: 1rem 0;">Focus</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem 0; color: var(--bright); font-weight: 600;">Brand · Web · Systems</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <td class="label" style="padding: 1rem 0;">Open to</td>
          <td style="padding: 1rem 0; color: var(--bright); font-weight: 600;">Freelance &amp; Full-time</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <td colspan="2" style="padding: 0;"></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Contact ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="contact" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem 6rem;">
  <p class="label fu" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Contact</p>
  <h2 class="display fu fu1" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem); margin-bottom: 4rem;">
    Let's make<br /><em>something</em><br />worth making.
  </h2>

  <div class="fu fu2" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start;">
    <div>
      <p style="color: var(--sub); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 36ch;">
        Open to brand identity projects, no-code web builds, and design consulting. I reply within 24 hours.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="btn btn-fire" style="font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 13px 28px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
        {{ site.email }}
      </a>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1.5rem;">
        {% if site.social.dribbble %}
        <a href="{{ site.social.dribbble }}" class="nav-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dribbble</a>
        {% endif %}
        {% if site.social.linkedin %}
        <a href="{{ site.social.linkedin }}" class="nav-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
        {% endif %}
        {% if site.social.twitter %}
        <a href="{{ site.social.twitter }}" class="nav-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Process card -->
    <div style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem 2rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">How I work</p>
      {% set steps = ["Discovery & brief", "Research & strategy", "Concept & iteration", "Delivery & handoff"] %}
      {% for step in steps %}
      <div style="
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.25rem;
        padding: 1.1rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        {% if loop.first %}border-top: 1px solid var(--border);{% endif %}
      ">
        <span style="
          font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic;
          font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 900;
          color: var(--fire); min-width: 1.75rem;
        ">{{ loop.index | pad2 }}</span>
        <span style="color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.88rem;">{{ step }}</span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
